@outofthebluebombay 🍽️ brings a vibrant vibe and global gourmet dishes that instantly lift your mood 🍕✨
From wood-fired pizzas to hearty sizzlers, the space truly comes alive – especially with their live jazz night every Saturday and unlimited Sunday brunch that’s perfect for laid-back indulgence 🥂🎶
If you’re staying at @lesutra 🏨 their widespread breakfast menu is perfect for morning start and the indoor dining is cozy and service is quick.

@thebluegourmetindia a charming patisserie serving handcrafted desserts and melt-in-the-mouth bakes 🍰💙
Their seasonal MangoHolic menu is a summer must-try, with refreshing mango mocktails, mains, and sweet treats that are equal parts indulgent and Instagram-worthy 🥭

Follow for more @jannatsorathia @dresstoeat
